      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Preparazione saldo da contabilita'                        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Esercizi con chiusura a fine anno (standard)              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-sdo-mag-std-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione e lettura                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rr-ann-ese           to   w-det-sdo-mag-ese      .
           perform   det-sdo-mag-nor-000  thru det-sdo-mag-nor-999    .
       det-sdo-mag-std-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-sdo-mag-ctr      .
       det-sdo-mag-std-420.
           add       1                    to   w-det-sdo-mag-ctr      .
           if        w-det-sdo-mag-ctr    >    12
                     go to  det-sdo-mag-std-900.
           if        w-det-sdo-mag-ctr    <    rr-mes-ini
                     go to  det-sdo-mag-std-420.
           if        w-det-sdo-mag-ctr    >    rr-mes-fin
                     go to  det-sdo-mag-std-900.
           move      rf-mms-prg-sca
                    (w-det-sdo-mag-ctr)   to   w-det-sdo-mag-sca
                                              (w-det-sdo-mag-ctr)     .
           move      rf-mms-prg-car
                    (w-det-sdo-mag-ctr)   to   w-det-sdo-mag-car
                                              (w-det-sdo-mag-ctr)     .
           go to     det-sdo-mag-std-420.
       det-sdo-mag-std-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-sdo-mag-std-999.
       det-sdo-mag-std-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Preparazione saldo da movimenti                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-mov-mag-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo conto           *
